{"tid":170740,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"太陽從東方昇起是否適用於南北極？","createTime":"2017-03-25T01:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T10:12:08.000Z","uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"73f56ef2855d10d8d9bf0fe19ace7363c2c49096","tid":170740,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:14:26.000Z","msg":"北極點應該得返南方 南極點又得返北方<br />\n<br />\n不過主要想問係極圈入面<br />\n因為南北極個日照時間唔係跟地球自轉<br />\n而係受地球公轉影響<br />\n其實太陽係咪會由其他方向升起？<br />\n<br />\n利申：睇完beauty and the beast"},{"pid":"24d9f29b963a7bdc1b1e7a2c770a64480ab1b59d","tid":170740,"uid":45645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:32:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c4eee8671f59206e13503c7345ce5dab3b99bfe","tid":170740,"uid":69348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:35:11.000Z","msg":"唔知點解係標題見到方東昇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"168eb9a801e7bfac4495c9074def79373f5ba851","tid":170740,"uid":34181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:36:54.000Z","msg":"雖然係認真問題<br />\n但係睇個標題總會覺得係膠問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b6abfc36eec7adbc14415fa4bf7750695d328df","tid":170740,"uid":48016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T02:52:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>北極點應該得返南方 南極點又得返北方<br />\n<br />\n不過主要想問係極圈入面<br />\n因為南北極個日照時間唔係跟地球自轉<br />\n而係受地球公轉影響<br />\n其實太陽係咪會由其他方向升起？<br />\n<br />\n利申：睇完beauty and the beast</blockquote><br />\n極晝期間你點先當升起"},{"pid":"07f8c70e2e73b0c7c4584feb446040df6766345e","tid":170740,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T10:12:08.000Z","msg":"南北極一年得一次日出日落<br />\n同一日亦係太陽喺正東升起同正西落<br />\n而喺南北極圈入面，日出依然係東方，日落依然係西方<br />\n因為你仲分到方位<br />\n但喺南/北極點上面就真係唔知點計"}]}